1
00:00:40,916 --> 00:00:44,041
[JOE] In the beginning
was the Voice,

2
00:00:44,125 --> 00:00:45,875
and the Voice was Him.

3
00:00:45,958 --> 00:00:49,416
And man would listen to
His Voice in great awe.

4
00:00:51,458 --> 00:00:56,083
But through vanity,
pride, deceit, and greed,

5
00:00:56,166 --> 00:00:58,583
man hoarded the
riches of the earth,

6
00:00:58,666 --> 00:01:04,708
raising a great many towers
whose tops reached unto heaven.

7
00:01:04,791 --> 00:01:09,041
As man's arrogance scattered
its people among ravaged lands,

8
00:01:09,125 --> 00:01:11,916
so was His Voice ignored.

9
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:15,625
Yet, He gave man
a chance to atone.

10
00:01:15,708 --> 00:01:17,041
[yelling and screaming]

11
00:01:17,125 --> 00:01:20,875
[JOE] And flame and smoke
and a great roar of lions

12
00:01:20,958 --> 00:01:22,708
fell upon the earth.

13
00:01:22,791 --> 00:01:25,750
[scattered yells]

14
00:01:25,833 --> 00:01:28,583
[JOE] Though pay heed,
listeners to His Voice.

15
00:01:28,666 --> 00:01:31,416
For some ordeals
waged in His honor

16
00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:34,958
may not force man
to hear as thou.

17
00:01:35,041 --> 00:01:37,500
[ANCHORWOMAN] On February 26,
at about 3:30 PM...

18
00:01:37,583 --> 00:01:39,333
[JOE] May the
devout bring justice

19
00:01:39,416 --> 00:01:44,708
to all people of the earth,
and let mankind start anew.

20
00:01:44,791 --> 00:01:47,375
May His Voice free us from sin

21
00:01:47,458 --> 00:01:51,583
and bless us with glory, honor,
and prosperity unending.

22
00:01:51,666 --> 00:01:52,875
[ANCHORWOMAN] At least
six buildings in total

23
00:01:52,958 --> 00:01:54,791
have now collapsed
throughout the area,

24
00:01:54,875 --> 00:01:58,166
with surrounding buildings
sustaining major damage.

25
00:01:58,250 --> 00:02:01,583
Fires and debris leave the
area in a state of confusion,

26
00:02:01,666 --> 00:02:05,041
severely impeding rescue
efforts. At this time,

27
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:09,500
we can only confirm that the
situation is far from contained.

28
00:02:09,583 --> 00:02:11,333
While it is too
early to determine

29
00:02:11,416 --> 00:02:14,125
an exact body count,
current estimates put

30
00:02:14,208 --> 00:02:17,500
the number of casualties
at least ten thousand.

31
00:02:17,583 --> 00:02:19,416
Chinese authorities have
declared the disaster

32
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:22,625
a terrorist act, and martial
law is currently in effect

33
00:02:22,708 --> 00:02:25,583
throughout Shanghai,
as no civilians are permitted

34
00:02:25,666 --> 00:02:27,791
to enter or exit the region.

35
00:02:27,875 --> 00:02:30,125
Today's tragedy appears
related to the series

36
00:02:30,208 --> 00:02:34,250
of suicide bombings that began
in America on January 16th

37
00:02:34,333 --> 00:02:37,125
with synchronized attacks
on Chicago's Willis Tower

38
00:02:37,208 --> 00:02:39,333
and Seattle's Columbia Center.

39
00:02:40,875 --> 00:02:42,875
The identity of those behind
the series of attacks...

40
00:02:42,958 --> 00:02:46,750
[JOE] Well planned. Must've been
in the works for some time.

41
00:02:46,833 --> 00:02:47,875
[ANCHORWOMAN]
...as none have come forward

42
00:02:47,958 --> 00:02:49,333
to claim responsibility...

43
00:02:49,416 --> 00:02:50,666
They've beaten me to it.

44
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:52,208
[ANCHORWOMAN] As for the
collateral damage incurred

45
00:02:52,291 --> 00:02:55,166
from the Financial Center's
collapse, experts say that...

46
00:03:12,291 --> 00:03:15,125
[JOE] Hey, Mom?
I'll be out late tonight.

47
00:03:17,541 --> 00:03:20,750
What? No, It's not a date
or anything like that...

48
00:04:55,375 --> 00:04:57,541
[WAITRESS]
Hello there.

49
00:04:57,625 --> 00:04:59,208
[GREAT BRITAIN]
Hello, Jet.

50
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:04,416
So now it's Shanghai, then.

51
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:07,708
Yeah, I've heard.
Been a while.

52
00:05:07,791 --> 00:05:11,833
Well, 9/11 was, what?
'Bout twelve years ago?

53
00:05:11,916 --> 00:05:12,916
How you holding up?

54
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,291
Haven't slacked
with my constant,

55
00:05:14,375 --> 00:05:18,166
pain-in-the-ass maintenance,
so not so bad.

56
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:20,750
[GREAT BRITAIN] Well, you're
sounding a little testy.

57
00:05:20,833 --> 00:05:22,208
Anything you want
to talk about?

58
00:05:22,291 --> 00:05:24,083
Just take your pick.

59
00:05:25,875 --> 00:05:28,958
The news spreads nothing
but paranoia lately.

60
00:05:29,041 --> 00:05:32,208
The President's baffled.
And now we've gotta

61
00:05:32,291 --> 00:05:36,291
come running just
'cause Gilmore says so?

62
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,708
I suppose.

63
00:05:40,791 --> 00:05:44,000
How can we blow off the guy
who made us what we are?

64
00:05:44,083 --> 00:05:48,041
Whenever there's trouble we
obey him, for the greater good.

65
00:05:48,125 --> 00:05:52,000
Zero-Zero Cyborgs don't
get to call their own shots.

66
00:06:03,458 --> 00:06:07,041
[JET] G.B., do you think
America was involved in this?

67
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,958
[GREAT BRITAIN] Actually,
I've got Israeli lobbyists

68
00:06:12,041 --> 00:06:14,166
saying my boys in
Parliment set it all up,

69
00:06:14,250 --> 00:06:17,458
as a great big gift to
our defense contractors.

70
00:06:18,583 --> 00:06:20,458
Well, that's today's gossip.

71
00:06:23,250 --> 00:06:26,000
So, what makes you ask?

72
00:06:26,083 --> 00:06:27,583
You're not having a
"crisis of confidence"

73
00:06:27,666 --> 00:06:30,041
in your lot's brand
of justice, are you?

74
00:06:33,791 --> 00:06:37,250
Hm. Forget it.

75
00:06:37,333 --> 00:06:39,583
If these bombings keep up,
everyone will get their turn

76
00:06:39,666 --> 00:06:43,416
at the blame game. Then
things'll really go to hell.

77
00:06:45,416 --> 00:06:48,041
And when they do, we'll all
have forgetten the times

78
00:06:48,125 --> 00:06:51,500
when nations could
keep each other in check.

79
00:06:57,291 --> 00:06:58,416
It's really coming down.

80
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,666
Sorry we're late.

81
00:06:59,750 --> 00:07:01,833
It's been a slow night.
Nothing to report.

82
00:07:04,125 --> 00:07:05,875
[TOMOE]
Joe, over here!

83
00:07:05,958 --> 00:07:10,541
[TOMOE pants]

84
00:07:10,625 --> 00:07:12,916
What do you know?
I thought I was the one

85
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,875
always dragging you out.

86
00:07:16,166 --> 00:07:19,041
I would stand out
too much coming alone.

87
00:07:33,708 --> 00:07:34,625
Huh?

88
00:07:34,708 --> 00:07:36,458
I love coffee.

89
00:07:42,166 --> 00:07:45,958
[TOMOE] You must be able to see
Tokyo Tower from your place!

90
00:07:46,041 --> 00:07:48,333
[JOE]
Not since Tower D went up.

91
00:07:48,416 --> 00:07:49,875
Huh?

92
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:56,791
Hey, how come you
ditched school today?

93
00:07:57,916 --> 00:08:01,166
We're on break.
What's the point of going?

94
00:08:07,916 --> 00:08:10,000
[TOMOE] Joe, I don't
think I've seen you talk

95
00:08:10,083 --> 00:08:12,875
with anyone else at school.

96
00:08:12,958 --> 00:08:16,416
Maybe we could try to hang
out with some of my friends?

97
00:08:17,791 --> 00:08:21,333
You act like you don't
want to be noticed, ever.

98
00:08:21,416 --> 00:08:24,708
Ah--! Why do you say that?

99
00:08:26,416 --> 00:08:28,625
Just been noticing.

100
00:08:28,708 --> 00:08:32,166
Ah... I never knew...

101
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:34,625
You've been keeping
an eye on me, huh?

102
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:09,291
Found you, 009.

103
00:09:11,541 --> 00:09:14,750
This probably sounds
like nonsense to you,

104
00:09:14,833 --> 00:09:17,541
but I feel like I've been
stuck in high school forever,

105
00:09:17,625 --> 00:09:20,375
and it just won't end.

106
00:09:20,458 --> 00:09:24,625
And it also feels like I've been
under observation all the while.

107
00:09:24,708 --> 00:09:28,791
Yeah, I know I felt that way
during my entrance exams.

108
00:09:28,875 --> 00:09:30,500
[JOE sighs]

109
00:09:30,583 --> 00:09:32,875
This is different...

110
00:09:32,958 --> 00:09:34,958
Really different...

111
00:09:35,041 --> 00:09:37,458
[JOE sighs]

112
00:09:37,541 --> 00:09:41,500
Also, how long have we been
going out now, anyway?

113
00:09:41,583 --> 00:09:45,583
I'm not even sure how long it is
you've been putting up with me.

114
00:09:45,666 --> 00:09:48,916
And if I honestly don't know
something that important,

115
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,250
then I guess I must have
already lost my mind

116
00:09:51,333 --> 00:09:53,375
a really long time ago.

117
00:09:55,708 --> 00:09:58,291
It's fine. Don't worry, Joe.

118
00:09:58,375 --> 00:10:01,041
C'mere. You're just tired.

119
00:10:06,708 --> 00:10:09,458
[JOE] I still have to
answer to His Voice.

120
00:10:09,541 --> 00:10:11,916
And deliver justice.

121
00:10:15,583 --> 00:10:17,833
[GREAT BRITAIN]
Jet, I need to ask you this

122
00:10:17,916 --> 00:10:19,916
strictly off the record.

123
00:10:21,166 --> 00:10:25,166
Have you heard of something
called "His Voice"?

124
00:10:26,541 --> 00:10:29,791
Whose voice do you mean?

125
00:10:29,875 --> 00:10:32,083
Not one government agency
has been able to find

126
00:10:32,166 --> 00:10:35,750
even a single connection between
any of the suicide bombers

127
00:10:35,833 --> 00:10:37,708
in their investigations.

128
00:10:37,791 --> 00:10:40,916
But there's been this one
phrase I've kept running into

129
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:45,041
ever since I began looking into
this mess here in the U.S.

130
00:10:45,125 --> 00:10:47,875
[JET] And that
would be "His Voice"?

131
00:10:47,958 --> 00:10:50,958
Right. Before the
two U.K. bombings,

132
00:10:51,041 --> 00:10:53,250
and the ones in
France and Hong Kong,

133
00:10:53,333 --> 00:10:56,833
each of these people
made some kind of noise

134
00:10:56,916 --> 00:11:01,083
about obeying "His Voice"
before blowing themselves up.

135
00:11:01,166 --> 00:11:04,750
They all said they wanted to
help mankind "start anew."

136
00:11:08,083 --> 00:11:10,041
Help us "start anew"?

137
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:21,250
So... Whose voice is it?

138
00:11:22,375 --> 00:11:26,416
Not a clue. A leader of some
kind of fundamentalist sect?

139
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:30,833
A syndicate boss backed
by Neocons? Hell, maybe it's

140
00:11:30,916 --> 00:11:35,166
some charmismatic sociopath
building up a crazy new cult.

141
00:11:35,250 --> 00:11:37,958
But considering we've
got no other connection

142
00:11:38,041 --> 00:11:41,250
between any of the previous
thirty-three bombers,

143
00:11:41,333 --> 00:11:45,291
this could be just the break
we've been looking for.

144
00:11:45,375 --> 00:11:46,958
I'll be handing this
to the appropriate

145
00:11:47,041 --> 00:11:49,083
intelligence agencies.

146
00:11:53,333 --> 00:11:54,958
Just thought you should know.

147
00:11:55,041 --> 00:11:58,083
Probably safest to keep
it to yourself for now.

148
00:12:00,166 --> 00:12:04,250
Cheers, Jet. Less work
talk next time, hm?

149
00:12:04,333 --> 00:12:07,708
G.B., you're really
meeting up in Istanbul?

150
00:12:09,166 --> 00:12:10,833
[GREAT BRITAIN] Well,
I can't exactly come and go

151
00:12:10,916 --> 00:12:13,500
as I please, now, can I?

152
00:12:13,583 --> 00:12:17,500
I'll make proper arrangements
with SIS before I pop off.

153
00:12:17,583 --> 00:12:19,375
I'm sure.

154
00:12:19,458 --> 00:12:21,041
So, how's he been?

155
00:12:22,250 --> 00:12:27,375
Remember, Jet: Butting in only
makes it worse with you two.

156
00:12:38,166 --> 00:12:41,291
Now what? He's out in public.

157
00:12:41,375 --> 00:12:43,083
[FRANCOISE]
Lure him up to the roof.

158
00:12:43,166 --> 00:12:46,500
Then do what you have to do.
And don't hold back.

159
00:12:59,166 --> 00:13:01,208
Incoming cruise missile?!

160
00:13:05,083 --> 00:13:07,625
What's wrong? Francoise?!

161
00:13:07,708 --> 00:13:08,916
[indistinct talking
and screaming]

162
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,500
[MAN IN BACKGROUND]
What's that?

163
00:13:10,583 --> 00:13:12,208
[TOMOE]
What?

164
00:13:12,291 --> 00:13:13,750
A bomb?!

165
00:13:24,375 --> 00:13:25,708
[FRANCOISE gasps]

166
00:13:25,791 --> 00:13:27,958
[GERONIMO JR.] What's going on?
Is it a suicide bomber?

167
00:13:28,041 --> 00:13:30,166
[FRANCOISE] No, this looks
like something else.

168
00:13:30,250 --> 00:13:33,333
Just get to 009
and wake him up!

169
00:13:33,416 --> 00:13:34,875
I'm on it.

170
00:13:40,708 --> 00:13:42,166
[JOE gasps]

171
00:13:43,250 --> 00:13:45,291
[GERONIMO JR. grunts]

172
00:13:45,375 --> 00:13:47,791
[JOE groans]

173
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:51,750
[JOE grunts]

174
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:03,875
[JOE pants]

175
00:14:12,625 --> 00:14:14,208
[JOE shudders]

176
00:14:14,291 --> 00:14:19,791
[JOE pants]

177
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:24,958
[GERONIMO JR. grunts]

178
00:14:26,833 --> 00:14:28,666
[GERONIMO JR. roars]

179
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:45,958
[FRANCOISE gasps]

180
00:15:01,583 --> 00:15:02,583
[GERONIMO JR. grunts]

181
00:15:02,666 --> 00:15:04,166
[JOE pants]

182
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:15,708
What is this?!

183
00:15:15,791 --> 00:15:17,791
Are you the one
doing all this?!

184
00:15:20,416 --> 00:15:21,333
[GERONIMO JR. grunts]

185
00:15:21,416 --> 00:15:23,541
[JOE grunts]

186
00:15:25,250 --> 00:15:26,416
[GERONIMO JR. yells]

187
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:28,625
[JOE groans]

188
00:15:34,250 --> 00:15:36,541
[GERONIMO JR. roars]

189
00:15:40,333 --> 00:15:41,791
[JOE gasps]

190
00:16:23,791 --> 00:16:32,208
[GERONIMO JR.
grunts repeatedly]

191
00:16:34,208 --> 00:16:35,708
[GERONIMO JR. grunts]

192
00:16:38,750 --> 00:16:41,458
[JOE]
Again?! What's going on?

193
00:16:56,375 --> 00:16:58,750
[JOE pants]

194
00:17:08,208 --> 00:17:15,250
[GERONIMO JR. growls]

195
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,458
[JOE]
Francoise!

196
00:17:31,541 --> 00:17:33,500
Activate Acceleration!

197
00:17:48,375 --> 00:17:51,333
[JOE pants]

198
00:17:51,416 --> 00:17:53,166
[JOE]
What were you thinking?!

199
00:17:56,041 --> 00:17:58,750
Hi, Joe. Welcome back.

200
00:18:07,416 --> 00:18:10,333
If you're here, then it means
we're all needed again.

201
00:18:10,416 --> 00:18:12,583
That's it, it's it?

202
00:18:12,666 --> 00:18:17,666
Yes. It is. Skyscrapers are
being attacked across the world,

203
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:19,875
and no one knows
who's behind it.

204
00:18:19,958 --> 00:18:23,000
It's time for Dr. Gilmore
to summon us again.

205
00:18:36,666 --> 00:18:38,541
So you're back?

206
00:18:38,625 --> 00:18:41,000
Mm. Been a while, Geronimo.

207
00:18:41,083 --> 00:18:42,875
Right.

208
00:18:42,958 --> 00:18:46,083
Was this another
suicide bombing?

209
00:18:46,166 --> 00:18:49,541
I don't know. But the
missiles were launched

210
00:18:49,625 --> 00:18:51,500
from an American vessel.

211
00:19:00,958 --> 00:19:02,333
[FRANCOISE gasps]

212
00:19:02,416 --> 00:19:05,458
[JOE] Their backup
generator finally kicked in.

213
00:19:05,541 --> 00:19:06,958
[FRANCOISE gasps]

214
00:19:07,041 --> 00:19:09,125
You seem to know
that building.

215
00:19:09,208 --> 00:19:10,666
[JOE]
Mm.

216
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:28,666
Pyunma, it sounds
like Jet doesn't know

217
00:19:28,750 --> 00:19:31,000
a thing about His Voice.

218
00:19:31,083 --> 00:19:34,416
And if Jet's not in the loop,
then His Voice is something

219
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:37,875
far more dangerous than
an American conspiracy,

220
00:19:37,958 --> 00:19:40,041
just like like you thought.

221
00:19:42,208 --> 00:19:44,916
Hm. I guess it isn't
just the President

222
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:47,291
who doesn't know what
the hell's going on.

223
00:20:26,458 --> 00:20:29,000
[AGENT grunts]

224
00:20:32,041 --> 00:20:35,291
[AGENT grunts]

225
00:20:44,041 --> 00:20:49,416
[AGENT groans]

226
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:50,958
[cracking noise]

227
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:03,916
[GREAT BRITAIN]
Hazra... Hm.

228
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:07,041
Bloody NSA... Hm?

229
00:21:26,750 --> 00:21:30,125
Cyborgs were supposed to fight
for justice, weren't they?

230
00:21:39,291 --> 00:21:40,750
[GREAT BRITAIN gasps]

231
00:22:22,166 --> 00:22:25,166
[phone rings]

232
00:22:26,625 --> 00:22:29,125
[phone rings]

233
00:22:29,208 --> 00:22:30,500
[phone chime]

234
00:22:30,583 --> 00:22:33,166
[JET]
It's me.

235
00:22:33,250 --> 00:22:35,250
Fired them into Tokyo?!

236
00:22:38,208 --> 00:22:39,833
He said that?

237
00:22:41,666 --> 00:22:43,375
"His Voice"?

238
00:22:49,250 --> 00:22:52,583
[JET pants]

239
00:23:24,500 --> 00:23:27,375
Chang Changku here.
Harbor infiltrated!

240
00:23:27,458 --> 00:23:29,708
Requesting further
intructions, Ivan.

241
00:23:29,791 --> 00:23:33,041
[IVAN] Understood.
I'm surprised you've accepted

242
00:23:33,125 --> 00:23:36,333
the Doctor's mission
so readily, 006.

243
00:23:36,416 --> 00:23:37,583
[CHANG]
Mm?

244
00:23:37,666 --> 00:23:39,208
[IVAN] It's unfortunate
that the legal dispute

245
00:23:39,291 --> 00:23:41,666
between you two
is still ongoing.

246
00:23:41,750 --> 00:23:43,333
Was it necessary
to trademark

247
00:23:43,416 --> 00:23:47,916
the name "Chang Changku" for
your restaurant franchise?

248
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:51,791
Hey, let's not dwell,
all right? Ah!

249
00:23:56,708 --> 00:23:59,458
The whole restaurant thing
might have rubbed Gilmore

