00:23:59,541 --> 00:24:03,583
the wrong way, but even us
cyborgs have got to eat.

251
00:24:03,666 --> 00:24:07,041
And fighting for justice
just does not pay the bills.

252
00:24:07,125 --> 00:24:09,083
As long as the Gilmore
Foundation gets

253
00:24:09,166 --> 00:24:13,125
a fat donation in my name
each year, all's fair!

254
00:24:13,208 --> 00:24:18,500
[CHANG grunts]

255
00:24:18,583 --> 00:24:22,583
So, how's this shipping company
connected to the bombings?

256
00:24:22,666 --> 00:24:26,958
Doesn't look like they're moving
anything suspicious to me.

257
00:24:27,041 --> 00:24:30,291
[IVAN] You've heard about
the Tokyo bombing, correct?

258
00:24:30,375 --> 00:24:33,875
Uh-huh. So we've really got
American cruise missiles

259
00:24:33,958 --> 00:24:35,583
in the middle
of all this now?

260
00:24:35,666 --> 00:24:38,541
[IVAN] Yes. That prompted
me to reinvestigate

261
00:24:38,625 --> 00:24:40,416
the initial attacks
in America.

262
00:24:40,500 --> 00:24:41,875
[CHANG]
Oh?

263
00:24:41,958 --> 00:24:45,041
[IVAN] And it appears that
this shipping company, SMO,

264
00:24:45,125 --> 00:24:46,416
had illegally sold off

265
00:24:46,500 --> 00:24:49,541
the collapsed buildings'
wreckage into China.

266
00:24:49,625 --> 00:24:50,916
[CHANG]
Wreckage from the attacks

267
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:53,750
would be pretty important
evidence, wouldn't it?

268
00:24:53,833 --> 00:24:56,500
[IVAN] Definitely.
And a civilian company

269
00:24:56,583 --> 00:25:00,833
sending evidence abroad, before
any proper examination, no less,

270
00:25:00,916 --> 00:25:03,375
is very suspicious.

271
00:25:05,041 --> 00:25:07,250
[CHANG]
Indeed it is.

272
00:25:26,875 --> 00:25:27,916
[CHANG]
Hwah!

273
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:33,250
[CHANG grunts]

274
00:25:57,416 --> 00:25:59,541
[CHANG] If Ivan's right
about this place,

275
00:25:59,625 --> 00:26:03,416
I should turn up some missile
fragments somewhere...

276
00:26:09,125 --> 00:26:11,500
[CHANG yells]

277
00:26:11,583 --> 00:26:15,916
[CHANG grunts]

278
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:22,666
[CHANG pants]

279
00:26:31,458 --> 00:26:32,958
[CHANG yelps]

280
00:26:39,458 --> 00:26:40,916
[CHANG]
Hraaah!

281
00:26:53,125 --> 00:26:56,000
[CHANG] Now, put your
hands behind your heads!

282
00:27:04,166 --> 00:27:05,625
[CHANG gasps]

283
00:27:08,291 --> 00:27:09,416
[CHANG yells]

284
00:27:09,500 --> 00:27:11,666
[CHANG grunts]

285
00:27:15,541 --> 00:27:18,583
[CHANG] So this is
how they operate?

286
00:27:18,666 --> 00:27:22,125
Blowing yourself up's even more
pathetic than using a missile!

287
00:27:22,208 --> 00:27:24,791
[CHANG coughs]

288
00:27:24,875 --> 00:27:28,958
[CHANG] God-fearing men
don't work this way!

289
00:27:29,041 --> 00:27:30,666
Despicable!

290
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:34,291
[CHANG growls]

291
00:28:23,625 --> 00:28:27,625
Again, I lived,
while you only waited.

292
00:29:06,583 --> 00:29:07,958
[HEINRICH] Wouldn't have
thought you'd settle

293
00:29:08,041 --> 00:29:11,875
into archeology, Pyunma.

294
00:29:11,958 --> 00:29:15,708
Well, the plan was for adventure
and glory. But as you can see,

295
00:29:15,791 --> 00:29:19,416
my schedule was wide open
when Dr. Gilmore called.

296
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:23,375
Although... if my
investigations in Africa

297
00:29:23,458 --> 00:29:26,708
really can help us out here,
it's all been worth it.

298
00:29:26,791 --> 00:29:27,875
[HEINRICH]
Damn right.

299
00:29:27,958 --> 00:29:29,875
Who needs glory, huh?

300
00:29:35,250 --> 00:29:38,166
I'm surprised you were
the first one to get here.

301
00:29:38,250 --> 00:29:41,375
So the GSG gives you
that much leeway?

302
00:29:41,458 --> 00:29:44,291
My whole body's made
of one-off parts.

303
00:29:44,375 --> 00:29:48,083
Some think I'm not even worth
the trouble to maintain. So...

304
00:29:48,166 --> 00:29:51,708
I'm not much more
than a Cold War relic.

305
00:29:51,791 --> 00:29:53,958
They'll still dust me off
to give demonstrations

306
00:29:54,041 --> 00:29:57,250
for the engineers.
But it's just a matter of time

307
00:29:57,333 --> 00:30:00,125
before they ship me
off to a museum.

308
00:30:02,791 --> 00:30:13,958
[various indistinct murmurs
among the crowd]

309
00:30:14,041 --> 00:30:17,583
Heh. It'll take us all
night to reach the lab.

310
00:30:21,208 --> 00:30:23,166
Hey, stop the jeep!

311
00:30:23,250 --> 00:30:25,041
[HEINRICH]
What's wrong?

312
00:30:25,125 --> 00:30:27,125
Pyunma!

313
00:30:27,208 --> 00:30:30,041
[PYUNMA pants]

314
00:30:37,250 --> 00:30:40,375
[PYUNMA gasps]

315
00:30:53,333 --> 00:30:56,416
Hey. Did a young girl
come through here?

316
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:09,958
[lively chatter]

317
00:31:35,166 --> 00:31:38,000
[PYUNMA gasps]

318
00:31:45,458 --> 00:31:46,833
[PYUNMA gasps]

319
00:31:46,916 --> 00:31:48,625
That's it.

320
00:31:48,708 --> 00:31:52,708
What they meant
by "His Voice."

321
00:32:39,916 --> 00:32:41,666
What in the hell...?

322
00:33:03,458 --> 00:33:04,625
[DR. GILMORE chuckles]

323
00:33:04,708 --> 00:33:07,416
[DR. GILMORE] It's good
to have you back, Joe.

324
00:33:07,500 --> 00:33:10,250
[IVAN]
It's nice to see you, 009.

325
00:33:10,333 --> 00:33:13,000
Yeah, 001. You too.

326
00:33:13,083 --> 00:33:15,333
It's been twenty-seven years.

327
00:33:15,416 --> 00:33:17,541
And of course you
haven't changed one bit,

328
00:33:17,625 --> 00:33:19,875
now, have you, Joe?

329
00:33:19,958 --> 00:33:22,541
Leading a normal life during
peace time could prove

330
00:33:22,625 --> 00:33:26,958
complicated with a body
like yours that doesn't age.

331
00:33:27,041 --> 00:33:29,666
That's why I've reset
your mind every three years

332
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:32,625
and locked away
your memories of us.

333
00:33:32,708 --> 00:33:35,083
I felt this would afford
you the stability needed

334
00:33:35,166 --> 00:33:37,833
to act as leader of
the Zero-Zero Cyborgs

335
00:33:37,916 --> 00:33:40,750
should ever the need arise.

336
00:33:40,833 --> 00:33:42,625
Looking back,
I believe my choice

337
00:33:42,708 --> 00:33:46,375
has burdened you,
nonetheless.

338
00:33:46,458 --> 00:33:48,708
What's important is,
you're here now.

339
00:33:48,791 --> 00:33:51,875
Yeah. Although I have to say,
repeating high school

340
00:33:51,958 --> 00:33:55,666
over and over had gotten
more than a bit stifling.

341
00:33:55,750 --> 00:33:57,708
You remembered it all?

342
00:33:57,791 --> 00:34:02,291
The memories from each reset
seemed to linger, somehow.

343
00:34:02,375 --> 00:34:05,625
And forcing you back here
cannot have helped matters.

344
00:34:05,708 --> 00:34:08,041
It's OK. I'm feeling
a little mixed up,

345
00:34:08,125 --> 00:34:10,083
but I can work through it.

346
00:34:10,166 --> 00:34:12,541
And the others! How are they?

347
00:34:14,416 --> 00:34:18,375
The rest all have formally
parted with the Foundation

348
00:34:18,458 --> 00:34:21,541
and sought out work
in their home countries.

349
00:34:23,333 --> 00:34:25,541
[DR. GILMORE sighs]

350
00:34:25,625 --> 00:34:30,000
However, Heinrich and Pyunma
have just arrived in Istanbul,

351
00:34:30,083 --> 00:34:32,291
and G.B. will join us once
he's received clearance

352
00:34:32,375 --> 00:34:35,500
from Britain's Secret
Intelligence Service.

353
00:34:35,583 --> 00:34:38,291
[IVAN] And we were
able to deploy 006

354
00:34:38,375 --> 00:34:42,125
on a special
reconnaissance mission.

355
00:34:42,208 --> 00:34:43,666
[JOE]
What about Jet?

356
00:34:43,750 --> 00:34:45,875
[DR. GILMORE]
Hmm...

357
00:34:45,958 --> 00:34:47,333
He couldn't still be--

358
00:34:47,416 --> 00:34:50,750
[IVAN] 002 now works for
the National Security Agency

359
00:34:50,833 --> 00:34:53,000
in the United States.

360
00:34:53,083 --> 00:34:55,250
I doubt that he would
ever be granted permission

361
00:34:55,333 --> 00:34:59,125
to team up with us again.
His absence is surely unrelated

362
00:34:59,208 --> 00:35:01,833
to any bad blood
between you two.

363
00:35:03,500 --> 00:35:08,416
Now, let me explain what
the NSA's involved with.

364
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:14,875
After the skyscraper bombings
originated in the United States,

365
00:35:14,958 --> 00:35:18,000
a great deal of conspiracy
theories had arisen.

366
00:35:18,083 --> 00:35:19,791
Obviously, several
of them suggest

367
00:35:19,875 --> 00:35:23,000
the U.S. government's
possible involvement.

368
00:35:24,333 --> 00:35:26,791
[IVAN] Have you heard
of Samuel Capital?

369
00:35:26,875 --> 00:35:30,166
It's a private investment
fund based in America.

370
00:35:30,250 --> 00:35:32,583
Though it acts on
behalf of its investors

371
00:35:32,666 --> 00:35:36,875
in Israel's Ministry of Defense.
Samuel Capital has one goal:

372
00:35:36,958 --> 00:35:39,500
to profit from the
military-industrial complex

373
00:35:39,583 --> 00:35:43,000
by undermining world
peace and stability.

374
00:35:45,458 --> 00:35:46,875
[Dr. GILMORE] The American
government seemed to have

375
00:35:46,958 --> 00:35:49,750
supported this agenda,
believing it would ultimately

376
00:35:49,833 --> 00:35:52,916
let the U.S. regain
global preeminence.

377
00:35:54,416 --> 00:35:57,250
My theory is supported
by Congress ignoring

378
00:35:57,333 --> 00:36:01,291
the illegal activities of
Samuel Capital's affiliates...

379
00:36:01,375 --> 00:36:05,166
chief among them being
the Post-Humanity Project.

380
00:36:05,250 --> 00:36:07,375
[IVAN] This includes the
development of cyborgs

381
00:36:07,458 --> 00:36:09,500
called Lazarus that are
made from the corpses

382
00:36:09,583 --> 00:36:14,208
of U.S. soldiers killed in Iraq,
as well as civilian casualties.

383
00:36:14,291 --> 00:36:16,458
Cyborgs from corpses?!

384
00:36:16,541 --> 00:36:19,208
[DR. GILMORE] Yes.
Chang's report will hopefully

385
00:36:19,291 --> 00:36:21,458
tell us more on
this matter, but...

386
00:36:21,541 --> 00:36:24,708
I suspect the initial
suicide bombings in America

387
00:36:24,791 --> 00:36:28,708
were carried out by these
Lazarus-type cyborgs.

388
00:36:28,791 --> 00:36:31,625
And by manufacturing
their own suicide bombers,

389
00:36:31,708 --> 00:36:35,000
Samuel Capital is poised
to control a new war,

390
00:36:35,083 --> 00:36:38,125
selling their exclusive
weapons and security services

391
00:36:38,208 --> 00:36:40,666
all across the globe.

392
00:36:40,750 --> 00:36:42,916
[IVAN] We believe the
United States government

393
00:36:43,000 --> 00:36:45,416
and Samuel Capital's
subversive plan

394
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:48,583
is the true cause of the
international bombings,

395
00:36:48,666 --> 00:36:51,583
and that the group charged with
facilitating this new means

396
00:36:51,666 --> 00:36:57,916
of remote warfare is the same
one employing 002: the NSA.

397
00:37:11,875 --> 00:37:13,750
[NAVYMAN] I'd failed
the U.S.-Japan-Korea

398
00:37:13,833 --> 00:37:15,958
military simulation
fifteen days ago.

399
00:37:16,041 --> 00:37:18,250
I haven't slept since then.

400
00:37:18,333 --> 00:37:22,875
That was the first day
I heard His Voice.

401
00:37:25,041 --> 00:37:28,750
In one moment, I was
addressing my C.O.

402
00:37:28,833 --> 00:37:32,666
And in the next, I could
hear it speaking to me!

403
00:37:32,750 --> 00:37:36,416
It was His Voice;
I had to answer!

404
00:37:36,500 --> 00:37:39,500
[INTERROGATOR] Exactly whose
voice are you talking about?

405
00:37:39,583 --> 00:37:40,958
[NAVYMAN shudders]

406
00:37:41,041 --> 00:37:42,541
[INTERROGATOR]
Hm?

407
00:37:44,875 --> 00:37:45,958
What's the matter?

408
00:37:46,041 --> 00:37:48,083
[NAVYMAN
breathes heavily]

409
00:37:48,166 --> 00:37:49,416
[INTERROGATOR]
Here, sit back down!

410
00:37:49,500 --> 00:37:50,583
[INTERROGATOR yells]

411
00:37:50,666 --> 00:37:54,500
[NAVYMAN chokes, gurgles]

412
00:37:54,583 --> 00:37:56,541
[INTERROGATOR] This bastard
bit his tongue off!

413
00:38:03,875 --> 00:38:06,666
[NAVAL OFFICER]
What's "His Voice"?

414
00:38:06,750 --> 00:38:11,166
And just how much intel do
you people have on all this?

415
00:38:13,875 --> 00:38:15,541
[FRANCOISE]
If Samuel Capital really is

416
00:38:15,625 --> 00:38:18,000
some new kind
of Axis of Evil,

417
00:38:18,083 --> 00:38:20,375
does this mean we'll be
going up against them?

418
00:38:20,458 --> 00:38:24,416
It's a strong possibility.
But before we take any action,

419
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:27,375
we first must understand
precisely how Samuel Capital

420
00:38:27,458 --> 00:38:31,958
was able to execute all 34
bombings across the globe.

421
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:35,416
And why the U.S. Navy
themselves fired a missile

422
00:38:35,500 --> 00:38:38,000
into Japan,
an allied country.

423
00:38:38,083 --> 00:38:42,125
These matters are
where we'll begin.

424
00:38:42,208 --> 00:38:44,958
But know that in a
worst-case scenario,

425
00:38:45,041 --> 00:38:49,083
we go up against the U.S.
military, as well as Jet.

426
00:38:49,166 --> 00:38:51,333
[GERONIMO JR. sighs]

427
00:38:51,416 --> 00:38:53,375
Doctor, I need to
ask you something

428
00:38:53,458 --> 00:38:56,541
about your research
into these attacks...

429
00:38:59,666 --> 00:39:02,583
Is it possible that all
of them were carried out

430
00:39:02,666 --> 00:39:05,583
by those answering
His Voice?

431
00:39:05,666 --> 00:39:07,083
[DR. GILMORE]
Hm?

432
00:39:07,166 --> 00:39:10,625
Before the global attacks
even began, while I tried living

433
00:39:10,708 --> 00:39:14,750
as a high-schooler, I heard
His Voice. That's why I was

434
00:39:14,833 --> 00:39:18,416
planning to bomb Roppongi
Hills, and answer Him.

435
00:39:19,750 --> 00:39:22,500
You had planned a
suicide bombing?

436
00:39:23,625 --> 00:39:26,041
[FRANCOISE &amp;
GERONIMO JR. gasp]

437
00:39:26,125 --> 00:39:30,166
[IVAN] 009, what do
you mean "His Voice"?

438
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:36,291
I guess it wasn't your voice
I heard, right, Doctor?

439
00:39:38,166 --> 00:39:40,833
I was answering the voice
so I could join the fight

440
00:39:40,916 --> 00:39:44,375
and help humanity
start over.

441
00:39:44,458 --> 00:39:46,333
What are you saying?

442
00:39:52,541 --> 00:39:56,166
Joe Shimamura,
is it really you?

443
00:39:59,541 --> 00:40:01,208
[FRANCOISE &amp;
GERONIMO JR. gasp]

444
00:40:22,625 --> 00:40:24,333
[JET] Even if the
Department of Defense

445
00:40:24,416 --> 00:40:27,166
benefitted from
Samuel Capital's plan,

446
00:40:27,250 --> 00:40:30,458
how could we let them
start a war on U.S. soil?

447
00:40:30,541 --> 00:40:35,208
An unmanned war,
with an unseen enemy.

448
00:40:35,291 --> 00:40:37,041
Did we know how far
things would escalate

449
00:40:37,125 --> 00:40:39,041
after the U.S. bombings?

450
00:40:40,708 --> 00:40:43,166
Regardless of what
we stand to gain,

451
00:40:43,250 --> 00:40:46,833
how can we let Samuel Capital
go unchecked, when this is

452
00:40:46,916 --> 00:40:51,166
growing into something we
may have no control over?

453
00:40:51,250 --> 00:40:53,625
Hell, this situation with
"His Voice" is starting

454
00:40:53,708 --> 00:40:56,166
to affect our
own soldiers now.

455
00:40:59,041 --> 00:41:01,750
So, what is His Voice?

456
00:41:01,833 --> 00:41:04,500
Another part of
Samuel Capital's plan?

457
00:41:04,583 --> 00:41:07,083
They're capable of anything,
from wiretapping

458
00:41:07,166 --> 00:41:10,541
to building weapons outta
corpses. Have they developed

459
00:41:10,625 --> 00:41:15,625
some kind of brainwashing
technology, too? And...

460
00:41:15,708 --> 00:41:17,583
...if they've got some
hidden agenda the NSA

461
00:41:17,666 --> 00:41:22,000
doesn't know about,
we're as helpless as anyone.

462
00:41:22,083 --> 00:41:24,583
[phone rings]

463
00:41:26,250 --> 00:41:28,625
[NSA OFFICER]
Jet, we've got an emergency.

464
00:41:28,708 --> 00:41:30,291
It's "His Voice" again.

465
00:41:30,375 --> 00:41:31,833
[JET gasps]

466
00:41:33,625 --> 00:41:36,375
Tell me where you heard
this "voice," Joe.

467
00:41:36,458 --> 00:41:40,625
Sorry, It's hard for me
to pin down where or when.

468
00:41:40,708 --> 00:41:43,750
I just know I was overcome
with this intense feeling

469
00:41:43,833 --> 00:41:45,666
that answering His Voice
was without a doubt

470
00:41:45,750 --> 00:41:48,541
the only way for me
to set things straight.

471
00:41:48,625 --> 00:41:51,000
That's why I thought it
came from you, Doctor.

472
00:41:51,083 --> 00:41:55,041
Hm, I see. So, are you saying
that the other bombers

473
00:41:55,125 --> 00:41:57,583
were responding to
this voice as well?

474
00:41:57,666 --> 00:42:00,583
Yes. If you look into
the Shanghai bombing,

475
00:42:00,666 --> 00:42:02,291
you'll see it was in
the works long before

476
00:42:02,375 --> 00:42:04,916
the initial attacks
on January 16th.

477
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:08,500
[IVAN] So you'd already
heard "His Voice" before?

478
00:42:08,583 --> 00:42:12,833
Hm. A few months beforehand.
It's clear others must have

479
00:42:12,916 --> 00:42:16,375
heard it and chosen
to take action as well.

480
00:42:16,458 --> 00:42:20,250
Hm...  What is His Voice?

481
00:42:20,333 --> 00:42:23,125
Francoise! Weren't you
the one watching Joe?!

482
00:42:23,208 --> 00:42:29,500
Uh... Yes. But to watch
every moment seemed a...

483
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:34,166
It's possible some sort
of virus may have infected

484
00:42:34,250 --> 00:42:38,291
the brainwave transmissions
used during his monitoring.

485
00:42:38,375 --> 00:42:41,041
Francoise, review all
data transmissions to Joe

486
00:42:41,125 --> 00:42:42,750
from the past three years.

487
00:42:42,833 --> 00:42:45,041
I'll need to scan
your brain, Joe.

488
00:42:45,125 --> 00:42:48,125
I ask for your cooperation.

489
00:42:48,208 --> 00:42:49,791
Geronimo.

490
00:43:02,208 --> 00:43:03,875
[PA] Doctor, we've
intercepted reports

491
00:43:03,958 --> 00:43:06,875
stating the U.S. Air Force
lost contact with a B-2 bomber

492
00:43:06,958 --> 00:43:10,375
three hours ago
over the Indian Ocean.

493
00:43:10,458 --> 00:43:13,875
The B-2 was last spotted
over the Arabian Sea.

494
00:43:13,958 --> 00:43:17,666
An F-38 fighter is now
in pursuit of the B-2.

495
00:43:17,750 --> 00:43:21,375
The pilot of the F-38
appears to be Jet Link.

496
00:43:21,458 --> 00:43:22,916
[JOE gasps]

497
00:43:40,916 --> 00:43:43,041
I'm a little busy here, guys.

498
00:44:01,416 --> 00:44:04,708
[muffled radio chatter]

499
00:44:45,750 --> 00:44:47,208
Sorry.

500
00:45:28,083 --> 00:45:29,458
[FRANCOISE]
I'm certain. It's Jet

501
00:45:29,541 --> 00:45:31,458
who left the
combat airspace.

502
00:45:33,291 --> 00:45:37,833
The B-2 is now crossing the Gulf
of Oman toward the Persian Gulf.

503
00:45:39,666 --> 00:45:43,125
Is it headed for Iraq?
What the hell's happening?

504
00:45:43,208 --> 00:45:47,666
The pilot in that B-2... I think
he also heard His Voice.

505
00:45:47,750 --> 00:45:50,583
He's probably
targeting Dubai!

506
00:45:50,666 --> 00:45:54,208
Are you saying this wasn't
planned by the U.S.?

507
00:45:54,291 --> 00:45:56,500
[JOE] If Jet was
deployed to stop it,

508
00:45:56,583 --> 00:45:58,708
I have to think it means
that the U.S. government

509
00:45:58,791 --> 00:46:01,375
is being forced
to take action!

510
00:46:01,458 --> 00:46:04,833
Doctor, have me teleported
to the pilot's airspace!

511
00:46:04,916 --> 00:46:06,041
[FRANCOISE gasps]

512
00:46:06,125 --> 00:46:08,791
I'll go, and find out
what's causing this!

513
00:46:08,875 --> 00:46:11,625
No! You just admitted to us
that you had planned

514
00:46:11,708 --> 00:46:16,958
a suicide bombing yourself!
I won't let you leave.

515
00:46:17,041 --> 00:46:21,666
Francoise, put me through to the
U.S. Department of Defense, now.

516
00:46:23,416 --> 00:46:26,750
Doctor, Joe is right. The U.S.
is being forced to act

517
00:46:26,833 --> 00:46:31,125
against whatever's
causing this. We have help!

518
00:46:33,958 --> 00:46:37,500
Ivan, we'll call Heinrich.
Teleport him to the scene.

519
00:46:37,583 --> 00:46:41,208
We'll have him shoot down
the B-2 if necessary--

520
00:46:41,291 --> 00:46:42,750
[DR. GILMORE gasps]

521
00:46:46,250 --> 00:46:48,958
Stop it!

522
00:46:49,041 --> 00:46:51,875
There's no way that
Heinrich can destroy a B-2.

523
00:46:51,958 --> 00:46:53,958
Given that much
speed and altitude,

524
00:46:54,041 --> 00:46:56,500
there's only two people
who can do this--

525
00:46:56,583 --> 00:47:00,666
me, with my Accelerator,
and Jet, who can fly.

526
00:47:02,416 --> 00:47:05,541
I have to find out
what His Voice is.

527
00:47:09,041 --> 00:47:10,625
Doctor...

528
00:47:12,250 --> 00:47:14,916
[IVAN]
Very well, 009.

529
00:47:26,583 --> 00:47:28,333
[no audible dialogue]

530
00:47:28,416 --> 00:47:30,250
[FRANCOISE gasps]

531
00:47:35,208 --> 00:47:37,083
How could this happen?

532
00:47:37,166 --> 00:47:42,500
Don't worry. I have faith
in Joe. Believe in him.

533
00:48:55,791 --> 00:48:58,583
Joe! I can handle this!

534
00:48:58,666 --> 00:49:01,666
Listen! I came for
the B-2's pilot!

535
00:49:01,750 --> 00:49:05,083
I wanna find out if
he heard His Voice!

536
00:49:05,166 --> 00:49:08,166
What did you say?!
You know about it?!

537
00:49:08,250 --> 00:49:11,541
So you're saying that you
already know about His Voice?!

538
00:49:13,916 --> 00:49:15,916
What's Gilmore
make of all this?

539
00:49:16,000 --> 00:49:19,000
He'd never heard of it.
He knows nothing.

540
00:49:19,083 --> 00:49:22,291
Dr. Gilmore thinks the NSA
and the whole U.S. government

541
00:49:22,375 --> 00:49:25,000
are behind all these bombings!

542
00:49:25,083 --> 00:49:26,583
Is Joe sending us this?!

543
00:49:26,666 --> 00:49:28,791
[FRANCOISE]
Mm.

544
00:49:28,875 --> 00:49:30,250
Well, then how do you know?!

545
00:49:30,333 --> 00:49:32,958
Because I heard
His Voice myself.

546
00:49:33,041 --> 00:49:35,875
I was actually planning
to bomb Roppongi.

547
00:49:35,958 --> 00:49:37,416
[JET gasps]

548
00:49:38,916 --> 00:49:43,916
My God, Joe...  Always on the
opposite corner, aren't you?

549
00:49:44,000 --> 00:49:46,500
I thought we were
friends until that day.

550
00:49:46,583 --> 00:49:48,916
But once we were
relieved from our duties,

551
00:49:49,000 --> 00:49:53,250
it was the Japanese wonder
boy the Foundation kept.

552
00:49:53,333 --> 00:49:56,083
A kid, put on global security?
And you're supposed to be

553
00:49:56,166 --> 00:49:59,375
the leader during a crisis?
You're a joke!

554
00:49:59,458 --> 00:50:03,291
Who protects peace and freedom?
America, that's who!

555
00:50:03,375 --> 00:50:05,083
I know. But does that mean

556
00:50:05,166 --> 00:50:08,666
it's the right thing
for the whole world?!

557
00:50:08,750 --> 00:50:10,875
Well, the right thing for me...

558
00:50:14,875 --> 00:50:18,875
...is to remove any
obstacles to my mission!

559
00:50:18,958 --> 00:50:21,416
[JOE] If you're not being
manipulated to do this,

560
00:50:21,500 --> 00:50:25,250
I'll back off. But if you are,
I'll answer His Voice

561
00:50:25,333 --> 00:50:28,875
and help this pilot
carry out his mission.

562
00:50:28,958 --> 00:50:30,250
[JET &amp; FRANCOISE gasp]

563
00:50:30,333 --> 00:50:32,541
He's going to help the pilot?!

564
00:50:34,333 --> 00:50:38,375
Joe, are you with us
or against us?!

565
00:50:45,791 --> 00:50:54,666
[JET &amp; JOE grunt]

566
00:50:56,291 --> 00:50:57,916
[JET gasps]

567
00:50:58,000 --> 00:50:59,625
[JET grunts]

568
00:51:01,500 --> 00:51:04,208
[JET pants]

569
00:51:04,291 --> 00:51:05,208
[JOE gasps]

570
00:51:05,291 --> 00:51:06,750
Look out!

571
00:51:19,125 --> 00:51:20,583
[JOE grunts]

572
00:51:22,583 --> 00:51:24,041
[JET gasps]

573
00:51:27,833 --> 00:51:29,291
[JET gasps]

574
00:51:48,041 --> 00:51:49,666
Joe!

575
00:52:13,250 --> 00:52:15,708
[honking]

576
00:52:31,666 --> 00:52:33,500
[indistinct screaming]

577
00:52:33,583 --> 00:52:35,041
[MAN yells]

578
00:52:52,708 --> 00:52:54,666
[indistinct screaming]

579
00:53:00,708 --> 00:53:02,166
[JOE]
Can this...

580
00:53:03,916 --> 00:53:08,666
Can this really be what
His Voice asked for?

581
00:53:34,625 --> 00:53:38,875
The B-2... was carrying
an armed nuclear warhead?

582
00:53:38,958 --> 00:53:40,458
Joe...

583
00:53:40,541 --> 00:53:45,708
[IVAN] 003, can you detect any
brainwave transmission from Joe?

584
00:53:45,791 --> 00:53:47,625
Too much interference.

585
00:53:50,000 --> 00:53:51,750
[IVAN] News of this
tragedy will spread

586
00:53:51,833 --> 00:53:54,125
across the world immediately.

587
00:53:57,083 --> 00:53:59,208
[DR. GILMORE shudders]

588
00:54:08,458 --> 00:54:13,833
Joe is dead now. What voice
could he have possibly heard?

589
00:54:13,916 --> 00:54:18,375
It seems that now we have
no way of ever finding out.

590
00:54:18,458 --> 00:54:21,666
[door opens]

591
00:54:21,750 --> 00:54:25,541
[IVAN]
004! 006!

592
00:54:25,625 --> 00:54:27,500
Sorry we're late.

593
00:54:27,583 --> 00:54:30,458
What a terrible
situation this is, no?

594
00:54:33,291 --> 00:54:34,958
And Pyunma?

595
00:54:36,375 --> 00:54:38,458
He disappeared today.

596
00:54:39,875 --> 00:54:42,166
But before that,
he'd actually found

597
00:54:42,250 --> 00:54:45,916
something that's
related to this mess.

598
00:54:46,000 --> 00:54:47,791
[IVAN]
What is that?

599
00:54:52,125 --> 00:54:56,083
Is this... the fossil
of... an angel?

600
00:55:10,333 --> 00:55:12,916
[MAN]
Yes, that's the situation.

601
00:55:13,000 --> 00:55:15,125
We should assume
that recon satellites

602
00:55:15,208 --> 00:55:17,041
have captured his
escape from Dubai.

603
00:55:17,125 --> 00:55:20,666
As well as his landing here
at Andrews Air Force Base.

604
00:55:20,750 --> 00:55:24,625
So concealing U.S. involvement
would be difficult.

605
00:55:25,666 --> 00:55:27,125
Yes, sir.

606
00:55:28,541 --> 00:55:30,291
[OFFICIAL] In that case,
we'll need to implement

607
00:55:30,375 --> 00:55:33,791
a suitable cover story
as soon as possible.

608
00:55:33,875 --> 00:55:35,833
Anyone have any ideas?

609
00:55:35,916 --> 00:55:38,166
[MAN] Actually...
The photos I sent?

610
00:55:38,250 --> 00:55:41,166
We leak them to media
outlets across the world.

611
00:55:41,250 --> 00:55:44,666
[grunting]

612
00:55:44,750 --> 00:55:47,500
I think I see where
you're headed with this.

613
00:55:47,583 --> 00:55:51,666
[MAN] We've spent a fortune
planning to use this failsafe.

614
00:55:51,750 --> 00:55:53,666
Now's the time, sir.

615
00:55:53,750 --> 00:55:56,958
[OFFICIAL]
And what about His Voice?

616
00:55:57,041 --> 00:55:59,708
[MAN] The B-2 pilot and
the soldiers who aided him

617
00:55:59,791 --> 00:56:01,750
have all been
taken into custody.

618
00:56:01,833 --> 00:56:03,083
Even as we speak
they're being questioned

619
00:56:03,166 --> 00:56:04,416
on the matter,
and, of course,

620
00:56:04,500 --> 00:56:08,708
a thorough investigation
is going to be conducted.

621
00:56:08,791 --> 00:56:10,708
[GUARDS pant]

622
00:56:10,791 --> 00:56:12,625
[GUARD]
Inform the commander.

623
00:56:19,916 --> 00:56:23,583
[JET] The NSA was sympathetic
to your companies' goals.

624
00:56:23,666 --> 00:56:26,291
And as such, they
gave you their direct

625
00:56:26,375 --> 00:56:29,125
and indirect support
at every turn.

626
00:56:29,208 --> 00:56:31,875
So I deserve some answers.

627
00:56:31,958 --> 00:56:34,625
Several U.S. military personnel
were directly involved

628
00:56:34,708 --> 00:56:37,500
in the last bombing.
And each one of them

629
00:56:37,583 --> 00:56:41,750
claimed to have heard
something called "His Voice."

630
00:56:41,833 --> 00:56:46,375
And if responsibility lies
right here at Samuel Capital,

631
00:56:46,458 --> 00:56:49,416
then you should be greatly
concerned, Mr. Klein.

632
00:56:50,541 --> 00:56:52,833
Now tell me what His Voice is!

633
00:56:54,041 --> 00:56:55,833
[KLEIN groans]

634
00:56:55,916 --> 00:56:57,958
[JET] The United States is
going to face accusations

635
00:56:58,041 --> 00:57:01,375
from the whole world because
of this latest bombing!

636
00:57:01,458 --> 00:57:04,875
We need to know what we're
dealing with here, and how

637
00:57:04,958 --> 00:57:08,250
our own troops are getting
dragged into all of this!

638
00:57:09,375 --> 00:57:11,250
[KLEIN]
Hm.

639
00:57:11,333 --> 00:57:14,291
This state of affairs has
only ever proven itself

640
00:57:14,375 --> 00:57:18,875
to be beneficial for us all.
Mankind is set on its path

641
00:57:18,958 --> 00:57:23,166
to begin anew, whether we
choose to intervene or not.

642
00:57:24,500 --> 00:57:26,833
What the hell
are you saying?

643
00:57:26,916 --> 00:57:30,833
You take issue with this?
All we've ever done

644
00:57:30,916 --> 00:57:33,750
is aided mankind by
answering His Voice.

645
00:57:33,833 --> 00:57:35,333
[JET shudders]

646
00:58:42,958 --> 00:58:44,583
[JOE sighs]

647
00:59:05,458 --> 00:59:08,333
I have been unable to
make contact with G.B.

648
00:59:10,916 --> 00:59:14,291
So, what? He's gotten
swept away by this "voice,"

649
00:59:14,375 --> 00:59:16,333
just like Pyunma?

650
00:59:16,416 --> 00:59:19,333
But what would the disappearance
of him have to do with G.B.'s?

651
00:59:19,416 --> 00:59:20,666
Hmm...

652
00:59:20,750 --> 00:59:23,416
Pyunma had discovered
that "angel fossil"

653
00:59:23,500 --> 00:59:27,833
while researching Olduvai
Gorge down in Tanzania.

654
00:59:27,916 --> 00:59:30,875
His notes say that,
as the skeleton was unearthed,

655
00:59:30,958 --> 00:59:32,625
more and more
of his dig staff

656
00:59:32,708 --> 00:59:34,833
claimed they'd started
hearing something.

657
00:59:34,916 --> 00:59:38,791
Something they'd only
refer to as "His Voice."

658
00:59:42,625 --> 00:59:46,333
[HEINRICH] They each
said the same thing...

659
00:59:46,416 --> 00:59:49,541
"In the beginning
was the Voice.

660
00:59:49,625 --> 00:59:51,708
And the Voice was Him.

661
00:59:51,791 --> 00:59:55,000
And man would
listen to His Voice.

662
00:59:55,083 --> 01:00:00,375
But through vanity,
pride, deceit, and greed,

663
01:00:00,458 --> 01:00:03,375
man hoarded the
riches of the earth,

664
01:00:03,458 --> 01:00:09,000
raising a great many towers
whose tops reached unto heaven.

665
01:00:09,083 --> 01:00:13,791
As man's arrogance scattered
its people among ravaged lands,

666
01:00:13,875 --> 01:00:16,666
so was His Voice ignored.

667
01:00:16,750 --> 01:00:21,416
Yet, He gave man
a chance to atone.

668
01:00:21,500 --> 01:00:25,500
And flame and smoke
and a great roar of lions

669
01:00:25,583 --> 01:00:27,416
fell upon the earth.

670
01:00:27,500 --> 01:00:31,458
And man's towers
were brought to dust."

671
01:00:34,125 --> 01:00:36,833
If it's biblical,
I've not heard it.

672
01:00:36,916 --> 01:00:38,750
[IVAN] That is because
there is no such passage

673
01:00:38,833 --> 01:00:41,500
in any version of the Bible.

674
01:00:41,583 --> 01:00:43,125
Pyunma knew that.

675
01:00:43,208 --> 01:00:47,250
So he figured his staff
came across this "voice" thing

676
01:00:47,333 --> 01:00:52,125
while they were all leafing
through some old apocrypha.

677
01:00:52,208 --> 01:00:56,250
But, as soon as the bombings
started on January 16th,

678
01:00:56,333 --> 01:01:01,000
Pyunma remembered.
Remembered every word they said.

679
01:01:01,083 --> 01:01:03,500
It was like those
words described

680
01:01:03,583 --> 01:01:05,333
all of the
skyscraper bombings

681
01:01:05,416 --> 01:01:08,416
that suddenly began
happening everywhere.

682
01:01:10,458 --> 01:01:13,833
And he knew that by
studying our origins,

683
01:01:13,916 --> 01:01:16,125
he was studying how we think.

684
01:01:16,208 --> 01:01:20,250
So, with that in mind, Pyunmna
hypothesized that his staffers

685
01:01:20,333 --> 01:01:23,166
had a kind of "religious
experience" when they saw

686
01:01:23,250 --> 01:01:26,166
that "angel" fossil,
an experience called

687
01:01:26,250 --> 01:01:29,708
"His Voice." And Pyunma
wondered if, in a way,

688
01:01:29,791 --> 01:01:32,750
they really had heard
a message from "God."

689
01:01:32,833 --> 01:01:35,916
So then, what do
we make of that?

690
01:01:36,000 --> 01:01:39,125
[HEINRICH] Hmm... Well,
this religious historian,

691
01:01:39,208 --> 01:01:43,166
Mircea Eliade, wrote about
some "mystical solidarity"

692
01:01:43,250 --> 01:01:46,666
between man and nature:
Hunting and farming had

693
01:01:46,750 --> 01:01:51,041
taught our ancestors about
the cycles of life. And death.

694
01:01:51,125 --> 01:01:54,125
Eliade thought that
understanding our connection

695
01:01:54,208 --> 01:01:57,625
with these cycles, is what
ultimately allowed our minds

696
01:01:57,708 --> 01:02:00,541
and our cultures to evolve.

697
01:02:00,625 --> 01:02:04,625
But the awareness of death
also led to the fear of death.

698
01:02:04,708 --> 01:02:07,666
In trying rationalize
such a huge mystery,

699
01:02:07,750 --> 01:02:11,916
people, you could say,
"invented" God.

700
01:02:12,000 --> 01:02:15,708
Freud also thought
religion came from the need

701
01:02:15,791 --> 01:02:19,875
"to shield ourselves from these
intimidating forces of nature"--

702
01:02:19,958 --> 01:02:22,875
things in life that
are too overwhelming.

703
01:02:25,541 --> 01:02:30,166
So, basically, just like our
ancestors "created" God

704
01:02:30,250 --> 01:02:34,541
out of their fear of death, we
had then "created" "His Voice",

705
01:02:34,625 --> 01:02:37,791
after seeing some damned
fossil that we did not know

706
01:02:37,875 --> 01:02:41,333
how to explain.
According to Pyunma.

707
01:02:42,375 --> 01:02:45,208
Let's say that the
suicide bombers believed

708
01:02:45,291 --> 01:02:46,625
His Voice was divine.

709
01:02:46,708 --> 01:02:49,250
So then, why is it that every
person who has heard it

710
01:02:49,333 --> 01:02:51,541
has gone on to
be a suicide bomber?

711
01:02:51,625 --> 01:02:53,833
It just doesn't make sense.

712
01:02:53,916 --> 01:02:57,166
Well. Stick with me,
because Pyunma's reasoning

713
01:02:57,250 --> 01:02:59,250
gets even stranger.

714
01:02:59,333 --> 01:03:03,166
He says, "in all of history,
no one's murdered more people

715
01:03:03,250 --> 01:03:05,333
for laughs than God."

716
01:03:05,416 --> 01:03:08,500
[DR. GILMORE] I understand.
But even if His Voice

717
01:03:08,583 --> 01:03:11,166
were actually some
kind of divine power,

718
01:03:11,250 --> 01:03:13,000
we mustn't overlook
the possibility

719
01:03:13,083 --> 01:03:16,875
that it's now being exploited
for political gains.

720
01:03:16,958 --> 01:03:19,708
That's true, governments
will exploit religion,

721
01:03:19,791 --> 01:03:22,416
like anything else.
A certain dictator

722
01:03:22,500 --> 01:03:26,333
from my home country
definitely comes to mind.

723
01:03:26,416 --> 01:03:29,583
Actually, one of the more
bizarre rumors surrounding

724
01:03:29,666 --> 01:03:33,500
"the Fuhrer" is that he was
compelled to wage the Holocaust

725
01:03:33,583 --> 01:03:37,166
in the first place after
he had come into posession

726
01:03:37,250 --> 01:03:39,458
of the fossil of an angel.

727
01:03:39,541 --> 01:03:41,000
Hmph.

728
01:03:42,375 --> 01:03:44,583
[HEINRICH] Pyunma had
asked G.B. to research

729
01:03:44,666 --> 01:03:48,750
that particular fossil.
The fact that G.B. has now

730
01:03:48,833 --> 01:03:52,916
also gone missing sounds
like more than a coincidence.

731
01:03:53,000 --> 01:03:55,041
[BOTH]
Hmm...

732
01:03:55,125 --> 01:03:58,458
Heinrich, if what you're
calling "God" is the product

733
01:03:58,541 --> 01:04:01,958
of a mind seeking
answers, then tell me:

734
01:04:02,041 --> 01:04:05,041
How can it intervene
so directly as to incite

735
01:04:05,125 --> 01:04:07,541
suicide bombings,
and to actually make

736
01:04:07,625 --> 01:04:10,791
some people
disappear altogether?

737
01:04:10,875 --> 01:04:12,791
[HEINRICH]
Good question.

738
01:04:12,875 --> 01:04:16,333
As he studied mankind's
origins, Pyunma eventually

739
01:04:16,416 --> 01:04:19,291
began to suspect that,
either through evolution

740
01:04:19,375 --> 01:04:22,333
or maybe the influence
of something else entirely,

741
01:04:22,416 --> 01:04:25,875
our minds had
actually become a God.

742
01:04:28,125 --> 01:04:31,416
[HEINRICH] He wrote, "Could our
human minds--these things that

743
01:04:31,500 --> 01:04:34,875
hold rational thought by some
fluke of nature--could they

744
01:04:34,958 --> 01:04:38,333
themselves be a 'God'?
What if our collective

745
01:04:38,416 --> 01:04:41,708
mind holds some unknown factor
that we've simply called "God"

746
01:04:41,791 --> 01:04:45,000
for lack of a better term?
What if this is the factor

747
01:04:45,083 --> 01:04:49,458
that's allowed us to
adapt, create, survive?"

748
01:04:49,541 --> 01:04:51,000
[FRANCOISE gasps]

749
01:04:52,541 --> 01:04:54,541
[JOE]
How can you be here?

750
01:04:57,166 --> 01:05:00,458
Hi, Joe! You okay?

751
01:05:00,541 --> 01:05:03,666
I've been worried about
you since the other night.

752
01:05:03,750 --> 01:05:05,833
[JOE stammers]

753
01:05:05,916 --> 01:05:08,875
Talk to me.

754
01:05:08,958 --> 01:05:11,166
[JOE sighs]

755
01:05:11,250 --> 01:05:15,916
Yesterday, a lot
of people died here.

756
01:05:16,000 --> 01:05:17,041
[TOMOE gasps]

757
01:05:17,125 --> 01:05:20,416
Oh, no... But
you're okay, right?

758
01:05:22,208 --> 01:05:25,333
I'm the only
one who lived.

759
01:05:25,416 --> 01:05:27,708
[TOMOE] That's weighing
on you, isn't it?

760
01:05:29,958 --> 01:05:33,166
[TOMOE] Don't worry, Joe.
God doesn't bestow burdens

761
01:05:33,250 --> 01:05:36,958
that we can't overcome.

762
01:05:37,041 --> 01:05:40,458
[JOE sighs heavily]

763
01:06:02,000 --> 01:06:06,500
Francoise... Tomoe was
a vision that you sent me.

764
01:06:06,583 --> 01:06:11,000
[thunder rumbling]

765
01:06:11,083 --> 01:06:14,708
If some God really existed
inside each one of us,

766
01:06:14,791 --> 01:06:18,333
maybe it could cause
Pyunma and G.B. to vanish...

767
01:06:18,416 --> 01:06:19,916
Although...

768
01:06:22,458 --> 01:06:27,208
If humanity is being incited
by a God that's within everyone,

769
01:06:27,291 --> 01:06:30,583
then why is it that only
a few have heard His Voice?

770
01:06:30,666 --> 01:06:34,083
And Joe, he never even
saw that angel fossil.

771
01:06:34,166 --> 01:06:37,166
How could he want to
become a suicide bomber?

772
01:06:37,250 --> 01:06:38,958
Hell if I know.

773
01:06:42,416 --> 01:06:45,875
[HEINRICH] But, all throughout
history, hasn't it been the case

774
01:06:45,958 --> 01:06:48,875
that only certain people
would go around claiming

775
01:06:48,958 --> 01:06:52,791
they could hear
the "voice of God"?

776
01:06:52,875 --> 01:06:54,875
People like
"spiritual mediums."

777
01:06:54,958 --> 01:06:58,666
Shamans, ascetics, martyrs;
they'd all claim to commune

778
01:06:58,750 --> 01:07:02,375
with the gods, after
facing "extreme trials."

779
01:07:02,458 --> 01:07:05,375
Today, when adventerous
types like racecar drivers

780
01:07:05,458 --> 01:07:08,375
or astronuasts face
intense overstimulation,

781
01:07:08,458 --> 01:07:11,791
they'll claim to feel some
"heightened sense of awareness."

782
01:07:11,875 --> 01:07:14,416
Maybe all of these
people felt the same thing,

783
01:07:14,500 --> 01:07:17,541
whatever that thing is...

784
01:07:17,625 --> 01:07:21,083
Then Joe, whose brain was
artificially enhanced.

785
01:07:21,166 --> 01:07:24,791
could be prone to some
"heightened awareness" too.

786
01:07:24,875 --> 01:07:28,458
Joe's brain was indeed under
an extreme state of tension

787
01:07:28,541 --> 01:07:31,375
during his leave, which may
well have caused some kind

788
01:07:31,458 --> 01:07:35,083
of synaptic anomaly that, in
time, Joe mistakenly began to

789
01:07:35,166 --> 01:07:38,125
interpret as
"His Voice," perhaps.

790
01:07:38,208 --> 01:07:40,500
[IVAN] "When this exists,
that comes to be;

791
01:07:40,583 --> 01:07:43,500
with the arising
of this, that arises.

792
01:07:43,583 --> 01:07:46,791
When this does not exist,
that does not come to be;

793
01:07:46,875 --> 01:07:49,708
with the cessation
of this, that ceases."

794
01:07:49,791 --> 01:07:53,208
Interesting how sutras even
after the Buddha's time

795
01:07:53,291 --> 01:07:55,708
would imply that
humanity and the divine

796
01:07:55,791 --> 01:07:58,583
have existed side
by side, always;

797
01:07:58,666 --> 01:08:02,708
us not creating it,
nor it us.

798
01:08:02,791 --> 01:08:04,625
[DR. GILMORE &amp; HENRICH]
Hmm...

799
01:08:04,708 --> 01:08:07,416
[distant explosions]

800
01:08:42,500 --> 01:08:45,000
[MAN] Do you have
anything new on "His Voice"?

801
01:08:45,083 --> 01:08:47,000
[JET] Yes, sir.
We need to get the word out

802
01:08:47,083 --> 01:08:48,416
as soon as possible.

803
01:08:48,500 --> 01:08:49,791
[MAN]
About what?

804
01:08:49,875 --> 01:08:52,625
About Samuel Klein.
His whole organization.

805
01:08:52,708 --> 01:08:56,125
They're... They're all
followers of His Voice.

806
01:08:56,208 --> 01:08:57,583
Hm?!

807
01:08:57,666 --> 01:09:00,500
[JET] What that means is,
the entire U.S. Congress...

808
01:09:00,583 --> 01:09:03,625
They're under the
control of His Voice, too!

809
01:09:03,708 --> 01:09:06,041
Oh... And?

810
01:09:06,125 --> 01:09:08,083
[JET gasps]

811
01:09:08,166 --> 01:09:11,041
And now, we have to prepare
countermeasure immediately,

812
01:09:11,125 --> 01:09:13,875
before this gets any
further out of control.

813
01:09:13,958 --> 01:09:15,333
Everyone has
to know that--

814
01:09:15,416 --> 01:09:19,083
I get it. Don't worry about
His Voice, I'll handle it.

815
01:09:19,166 --> 01:09:22,833
But we have to deal with
the Dubai incident first.

816
01:09:22,916 --> 01:09:25,416
[JET gasps]

817
01:09:25,500 --> 01:09:28,083
The man who, made you
a cyborg, Dr. Gilmore...

818
01:09:28,166 --> 01:09:31,625
He's currently operating
out of Istanbul, is he not?

819
01:09:31,708 --> 01:09:33,125
Have you been in
contact with him

820
01:09:33,208 --> 01:09:35,958
or his "Foundation" recently?

821
01:09:36,041 --> 01:09:37,916
What are
you saying?

822
01:09:38,000 --> 01:09:39,875
We've identifided
the two terrorists

823
01:09:39,958 --> 01:09:42,625
responsible for attacking Dubai.

824
01:09:44,333 --> 01:09:45,541
[JET]
Bastard!

825
01:09:45,625 --> 01:09:47,958
[JET grunts]

826
01:09:50,166 --> 01:09:52,583
[blows landing]

827
01:09:52,666 --> 01:09:54,166
[taser crackling]

828
01:09:54,250 --> 01:09:56,458
[blows landing]

829
01:09:56,541 --> 01:10:04,166
[JET grunts]

830
01:10:08,291 --> 01:10:11,166
Your old friends are likely
experiencing the same thing

831
01:10:11,250 --> 01:10:14,791
right about now. We thank you
for your service, Agent Link.

832
01:10:14,875 --> 01:10:17,291
You're about to embark
on your final mission.

833
01:10:17,375 --> 01:10:20,541
[JET quietly whimpering]

834
01:10:24,916 --> 01:10:26,375
[JET gasps]

835
01:10:29,291 --> 01:10:32,208
[screaming]

836
01:10:36,250 --> 01:10:46,041
[alarms blaring,
police sirens wailing]

837
01:10:46,125 --> 01:10:47,583
[JET gasps]

838
01:11:04,875 --> 01:11:06,833
[PA SYSTEM] Hostiles closing
in from both ground level

839
01:11:06,916 --> 01:11:09,708
and rooftop. Number: unknown.

840
01:11:13,916 --> 01:11:15,375
[CHANG yells]

841
01:11:21,208 --> 01:11:24,791
Use these. I'll take the
ones coming in from the roof.

842
01:11:26,625 --> 01:11:28,083
Hrrgh!

843
01:11:32,708 --> 01:11:35,125
Urgh!

844
01:11:35,208 --> 01:11:36,750
Pwoogh!

845
01:12:15,875 --> 01:12:17,791
[STAFF scream]

846
01:12:21,583 --> 01:12:23,625
[FEMALE STAFF scream]

847
01:12:31,625 --> 01:12:33,708
Haaah!

848
01:12:33,791 --> 01:12:37,666
[CHANG screams]

849
01:12:40,416 --> 01:12:42,750
[CHANG screams]

850
01:12:49,166 --> 01:12:50,625
[GERONIMO JR.]
Hmph!

851
01:13:01,250 --> 01:13:03,708
Hmph. Rrgh!

852
01:13:08,166 --> 01:13:13,375
[GERONIMO JR. growls]

853
01:13:18,583 --> 01:13:20,458
[GERONIMO JR.]
Rraagh!

854
01:13:20,541 --> 01:13:22,083
Haagh!

855
01:13:31,875 --> 01:13:33,333
[GERONIMO JR.]
Raagh!

856
01:13:38,333 --> 01:13:40,500
[panting]

857
01:13:45,916 --> 01:13:51,750
[GERONIMO JR. roars]

858
01:13:54,708 --> 01:13:56,333
[GUARD A]
Hey!

859
01:13:56,416 --> 01:14:00,375
Hey, y-you all right?!
C'mon, I gotcha.

860
01:14:01,916 --> 01:14:05,875
[GUARD gasps, stutters]

861
01:14:05,958 --> 01:14:07,416
[JET]
Hey!

862
01:14:10,291 --> 01:14:12,500
[radio chatter]

863
01:14:26,083 --> 01:14:28,583
[RADIO] We've sustained
heavy casualties down here!

864
01:14:32,208 --> 01:14:33,583
Right here...

865
01:15:01,250 --> 01:15:04,208
[JET]
Ah! What the hell?!

866
01:15:04,291 --> 01:15:05,750
My God...

867
01:15:15,458 --> 01:15:16,916
[gasps]

868
01:15:33,125 --> 01:15:35,791
[JET] What did they...
make me do?

869
01:15:43,416 --> 01:15:48,166
[indistinct yelling
among OFFICIALS]

870
01:15:48,250 --> 01:15:51,125
Even more people are hearing
this damn voice now.

871
01:15:51,208 --> 01:15:52,666
[GUARD]
Don't move!

872
01:15:54,125 --> 01:15:56,500
I do not have
time for this, kid!

873
01:16:08,333 --> 01:16:11,041
I wish they'd let up already!

874
01:16:11,125 --> 01:16:13,541
How many of these
damn things are there?!

875
01:16:16,583 --> 01:16:19,125
Doctor! I have
a signal from Joe!

876
01:16:19,208 --> 01:16:21,208
What?! Joe is alive?!

877
01:16:21,291 --> 01:16:24,583
Yes. He's sending me
his coordinates right now.

878
01:16:25,875 --> 01:16:28,208
[IVAN] So he wants me to
teleport him back here?

879
01:16:28,291 --> 01:16:31,875
Now I'm getting
a signal from 002!

880
01:16:31,958 --> 01:16:36,083
[FRANCOISE] He's asking that
we open a channel for him.

881
01:16:36,166 --> 01:16:39,916
[JET] Dr. Gilmore,
moments ago, a United States

882
01:16:40,000 --> 01:16:42,166
Naval nuclear subarine
declared their intention

883
01:16:42,250 --> 01:16:46,750
to "help humanity start anew,
in answer to His Voice."

884
01:16:46,833 --> 01:16:48,416
Now, they've gone silent.

885
01:16:48,500 --> 01:16:55,375
The Pentagon and the White House
are scrambling to locate it.

886
01:16:55,458 --> 01:16:59,458
They won't find it.
They're too late.

887
01:16:59,541 --> 01:17:02,833
[DR. GILMORE] What is the U.S.
Government's role in all this?

888
01:17:02,916 --> 01:17:08,750
They wanted to... blame us
Zero-Zero Cyborgs for...

889
01:17:08,833 --> 01:17:12,875
They wanted to blame us
for all of the bombings.

890
01:17:12,958 --> 01:17:16,291
But they can't stop
more from coming...

891
01:17:16,375 --> 01:17:22,041
Doctor, you always believed
that he was the one who could

892
01:17:22,125 --> 01:17:24,583
stop something like
this, didn't you?

893
01:17:24,666 --> 01:17:28,708
Doctor! Before he was
teleported, Joe whispered,

894
01:17:28,791 --> 01:17:31,583
"I know Jet's not our enemy."
And when Joe said he'd

895
01:17:31,666 --> 01:17:36,458
answer His Voice, and...
and help that B-2 pilot...

896
01:17:36,541 --> 01:17:39,750
it was to prove Jet wasn't
involved! Because Joe never

897
01:17:39,833 --> 01:17:43,000
lost faith in his teammate!
In spite of everything,

898
01:17:43,083 --> 01:17:45,250
Joe has only fought for justice!

899
01:17:45,333 --> 01:17:47,791
I know in my heart that
Joe can save us all,

900
01:17:47,875 --> 01:17:50,291
if you'll just believe in him.

901
01:18:01,083 --> 01:18:05,625
[JET grunts]

902
01:18:10,125 --> 01:18:12,583
Now what?
They'll break through...

903
01:18:31,583 --> 01:18:33,041
Hmm.

904
01:18:38,083 --> 01:18:39,541
[HEINRICH gasps]

905
01:18:41,375 --> 01:18:42,833
[CHANG gasps]

906
01:19:26,416 --> 01:19:31,833
[WOMAN whimpers]

907
01:19:44,625 --> 01:19:46,458
[FRANCOISE gasps]

908
01:19:46,541 --> 01:19:48,000
[FRANCOISE]
Joe!

909
01:19:50,500 --> 01:19:53,000
[JOE] I'm so sorry
I made you worry.

910
01:19:53,083 --> 01:19:55,375
I'm glad you're all right.

911
01:19:55,458 --> 01:19:59,791
When the nuke exploded in Dubai,
I was so ashamed that I lived

912
01:19:59,875 --> 01:20:02,291
when all those other
people didn't make it.

913
01:20:02,375 --> 01:20:05,625
But I know why I
really lived now.

914
01:20:05,708 --> 01:20:09,375
It's because of you, Francoise.

915
01:20:09,458 --> 01:20:13,458
And His Voice... I can hear
it in a different way now.

916
01:20:13,541 --> 01:20:18,291
Doctor. I'm going to go stop
that submarine, no matter what.

917
01:20:18,375 --> 01:20:20,333
Can you arrange things?

918
01:20:20,416 --> 01:20:21,875
Hm.

919
01:20:26,750 --> 01:20:29,458
[CHANG] The subarine went
dark fifteen minutes ago.

920
01:20:29,541 --> 01:20:31,666
Even at its top speed,
it can't have gone

921
01:20:31,750 --> 01:20:33,791
any farther than this, right?

922
01:20:33,875 --> 01:20:35,916
[IVAN] Without the submarine's
exact coordinates,

923
01:20:36,000 --> 01:20:39,416
I'm not able to
teleport you inside of it.

924
01:20:39,500 --> 01:20:42,333
But, if they're following
standard procedure,

925
01:20:42,416 --> 01:20:44,750
just like Jet has been
telling us they are,

926
01:20:44,833 --> 01:20:46,625
they'll be launching
their nuclear missiles

927
01:20:46,708 --> 01:20:48,666
in just fifteen minutes!

928
01:20:50,375 --> 01:20:51,833
What are our options?

929
01:20:53,625 --> 01:20:56,208
[FRANCOISE] The U.S.S. Sentinel
carries interceptor missiles.

930
01:20:56,291 --> 01:20:58,458
It's off the
coast of Hawaii.

931
01:20:58,541 --> 01:21:00,791
[DR. GILMORE] All right,
then. We take the ship.

932
01:22:30,166 --> 01:22:31,625
[CREWMAN gasps]

933
01:23:04,458 --> 01:23:08,500
Attention: I'm opening missile
tubes. Prepare to fire...

934
01:23:18,208 --> 01:23:19,666
[SUBMARINE OFFICER]
No!

935
01:23:21,041 --> 01:23:25,458
[OFFICERS grunt]

936
01:23:28,083 --> 01:23:29,541
[GERONIMO JR. growls]

937
01:23:33,125 --> 01:23:34,166
[CHANG]
You all right?!

938
01:23:34,250 --> 01:23:35,583
[GERONIMO JR. grunts]

939
01:23:35,666 --> 01:23:37,166
The nukes haven't launched yet?

940
01:23:37,250 --> 01:23:40,791
[IVAN] No, not yet, Doctor. The
deployment of nuclear missiles

941
01:23:40,875 --> 01:23:43,916
requires multiple
authorizations. It's possible

942
01:23:44,000 --> 01:23:47,333
there's some unrest within
the submarine's crew.

943
01:23:52,958 --> 01:23:54,708
[HEINRICH] I'd really
like to trust you guys.

944
01:23:54,791 --> 01:23:56,708
Unfortunately, I cannot.

945
01:24:17,250 --> 01:24:18,708
They fired them!

946
01:25:02,583 --> 01:25:05,875
[FRANCOISE]
Six... Five... Four...

947
01:25:05,958 --> 01:25:08,083
Intercepting targets now!

948
01:25:18,291 --> 01:25:20,291
It worked?!

949
01:25:20,375 --> 01:25:21,833
[JOE gasps]

950
01:25:22,875 --> 01:25:24,333
[FRANCOISE]
One left...

951
01:25:35,625 --> 01:25:37,083
We missed the last nuke!

952
01:25:52,833 --> 01:25:54,916
Francoise...

953
01:25:55,000 --> 01:25:57,458
You can calculate the
missile's trajectory, right?

954
01:26:00,000 --> 01:26:04,458
[JOE] It looks like we'll have
to detonate it. Manually.

955
01:26:04,541 --> 01:26:08,250
And you're going to do it
yourself? Joe, you can't!

956
01:26:08,333 --> 01:26:11,750
Even if you succeed, you won't
make it down from that altitude!

957
01:26:11,833 --> 01:26:13,500
I know that.

958
01:26:13,583 --> 01:26:15,291
Then, why?!

959
01:26:15,375 --> 01:26:19,375
Francoise. My life was spared
so that I could do this.

960
01:26:26,291 --> 01:26:28,208
[FRANCOISE quietly whimpers]

961
01:26:30,208 --> 01:26:32,500
[FRANCOISE] Ivan.
Please teleport Joe

962
01:26:32,583 --> 01:26:34,541
to the coordintes I'm sending.

963
01:26:39,000 --> 01:26:41,916
[IVAN] Are you positive,
Francoise? I won't have

964
01:26:42,000 --> 01:26:45,541
the strength for another
teleportation after this.

965
01:26:47,875 --> 01:26:49,333
[FRANCOISE]
Please...

966
01:27:48,125 --> 01:27:49,583
[JOE gasps]

967
01:28:40,500 --> 01:28:42,583
[HEINRICH]
It's still there!

968
01:28:42,666 --> 01:28:44,708
Joe!

969
01:28:44,791 --> 01:28:49,041
[FRANCOISE sobs quietly,
HEINRICH sighs]

970
01:28:49,125 --> 01:28:50,208
[BOTH gasp]

971
01:28:50,291 --> 01:28:52,791
Something is closing in on it!

972
01:28:52,875 --> 01:28:54,333
[BOTH gasp]

973
01:29:12,000 --> 01:29:14,333
[JOE gasps]

974
01:29:14,416 --> 01:29:17,000
[JOE] Jet! What are
you doing here?!

975
01:29:17,083 --> 01:29:20,416
[JET] I've been listening in on
the brainwave transmissions.

976
01:29:20,500 --> 01:29:22,125
Give me the charges!

977
01:29:22,208 --> 01:29:25,083
[BOTH grunt]

978
01:29:27,458 --> 01:29:31,041
[JOE] Forget it! There's still
time for you to make it back!

979
01:29:37,166 --> 01:29:40,958
[JET] Joe, even if you stop
the nuke, there's no guarantee

980
01:29:41,041 --> 01:29:43,375
you'll stop His Voice.
Are you sure you want

981
01:29:43,458 --> 01:29:44,958
to go through with this?

982
01:29:45,041 --> 01:29:47,708
[JOE] Everyone answers
His Voice differently,

983
01:29:47,791 --> 01:29:50,958
based on their frame of mind.
If we show people

984
01:29:51,041 --> 01:29:53,375
they can stand up to
this kind of answer,

985
01:29:53,458 --> 01:29:56,041
they might join us
in fighting for peace!

986
01:29:57,833 --> 01:30:01,375
[JET] And you believe that's
what His Voice really wanted?

987
01:30:01,458 --> 01:30:05,375
[JOE] Maybe. Enough to know that
this is the right decision!

988
01:30:14,083 --> 01:30:19,708
[BOTH grunt]

989
01:30:19,791 --> 01:30:21,666
[grunting continues]

990
01:30:24,666 --> 01:30:27,500
[JOE grunts]

991
01:30:27,583 --> 01:30:30,875
[JET yells]

992
01:30:33,416 --> 01:30:36,458
[JOE] We did it!
Jet, I'm on!

993
01:30:36,541 --> 01:30:38,000
[JOE gasps]

994
01:30:46,666 --> 01:30:51,041
No! Jet!!

995
01:30:59,291 --> 01:31:01,250
[JOE groans]

996
01:31:04,041 --> 01:31:06,875
[JOE] It's true, people
can be foolish...

997
01:31:06,958 --> 01:31:09,416
In groups, we easily
get corrupted

998
01:31:09,500 --> 01:31:11,708
by some collective mind...

999
01:31:13,458 --> 01:31:15,958
One that we can't
seem to resist.

1000
01:31:18,166 --> 01:31:21,333
We aren't perfect,
but that means we also

1001
01:31:21,416 --> 01:31:23,833
have so much potential.

1002
01:31:23,916 --> 01:31:27,083
We've done terrible things
together, but we can do

1003
01:31:27,166 --> 01:31:33,333
great together as well.
That's what makes us worth it!

1004
01:31:33,416 --> 01:31:36,875
Are you really going
to crush the hopes

1005
01:31:36,958 --> 01:31:39,958
of all the people who've risked
everything, risked their lives,

1006
01:31:40,041 --> 01:31:43,416
trying to answer your
call to save this world?!

1007
01:31:43,500 --> 01:31:47,000
How can you look down on
all that's good about us

1008
01:31:47,083 --> 01:31:50,875
and destroy us anyway?!

1009
01:31:50,958 --> 01:31:52,833
Give me an answer...

1010
01:31:55,708 --> 01:31:58,541
...God!

1011
01:32:35,458 --> 01:32:37,750
[IVAN grunts softly
in his sleep]

1012
01:32:40,916 --> 01:32:44,125
[soft grunting continues]

1013
01:33:09,166 --> 01:33:17,250
[FRANCOISE sobs softly]

1014
01:33:48,000 --> 01:33:51,375
[grunting]

1015
01:33:51,458 --> 01:33:52,916
[startled gasp]

1016
01:33:59,291 --> 01:34:00,750
[JOE sighs]

1017
01:34:32,416 --> 01:34:33,875
[JOE]
Hmm...

1018
01:34:44,333 --> 01:34:45,791
[JOE gasps]

1019
01:34:55,416 --> 01:34:57,083
[JOE gasps]

1020
01:35:01,625 --> 01:35:03,250
[door creaking open]

1021
01:35:17,500 --> 01:35:21,666
Ah. Good,
you're up.

1022
01:35:21,750 --> 01:35:24,875
Yeah, but where are we?

1023
01:35:24,958 --> 01:35:27,375
This place? We're
in my safe house.

1024
01:35:27,458 --> 01:35:29,000
Safe house?

1025
01:35:30,583 --> 01:35:35,125
What am I doing here? Francoise,
how did I get back down?

1026
01:35:36,666 --> 01:35:40,791
[FRANCOISE] I guess...
it's a mystery.

1027
01:35:40,875 --> 01:35:42,625
But the very fact
that you're here

1028
01:35:42,708 --> 01:35:44,916
means He answered
you this time.

1029
01:35:47,083 --> 01:35:50,166
Didn't the missile--?
Wait, where's Jet?!

1030
01:36:35,416 --> 01:36:38,125
[GREAT BRITAIN]
Pyunma? Fancy that.

1031
01:36:38,208 --> 01:36:40,958
[PYUNMA] I know. I found
myself here when I came to.

1032
01:36:41,041 --> 01:36:43,666
[JET] And where
exactly is "here?"

1033
01:36:47,000 --> 01:36:50,958
Well, if you guys made it,
maybe it's Heaven?

1034
01:36:55,375 --> 01:36:57,916
[DR. GILMORE] No. This is
the exact same world

1035
01:36:58,000 --> 01:37:00,250
you boys helped save.

1036
01:37:01,291 --> 01:37:03,375
It's good to have
you back with us.

1037
01:37:03,458 --> 01:37:06,250
You should know that I
am very proud of you all.

1038
01:37:07,958 --> 01:37:09,708
How'd we get here?

1039
01:37:09,791 --> 01:37:12,041
"His Voice" did this?

1040
01:37:12,125 --> 01:37:14,708
Who knows? Maybe we're all here

1041
01:37:14,791 --> 01:37:18,875
because someone who had heard
His Voice asked loud enough.

1042
01:37:20,291 --> 01:37:24,125
Even if that's true, what the
hell are we supposed to do next?

1043
01:37:24,208 --> 01:37:28,291
This isn't over.
The fighting will only continue.

1044
01:37:28,375 --> 01:37:30,833
Our world has indeed
been gravely affected

1045
01:37:30,916 --> 01:37:34,250
by the atrocities commited
in answer to "His Voice."

1046
01:37:34,333 --> 01:37:37,416
So then, doesn't that make
it all the more necessary

1047
01:37:37,500 --> 01:37:39,666
that you continue to
fight for the justice

1048
01:37:39,750 --> 01:37:42,000
you have always believed in?

1049
01:37:49,708 --> 01:37:57,333
[bells ringing,
children laughing]

1050
01:37:57,416 --> 01:38:00,208
[FRANCOISE] You know, as I
watched those shooting stars,

1051
01:38:00,291 --> 01:38:02,291
I thought, maybe...

1052
01:38:02,375 --> 01:38:04,208
His Voice doesn't
bestow burdens

1053
01:38:04,291 --> 01:38:06,750
that humanity
can't overcome.

1054
01:38:10,958 --> 01:38:12,416
[JOE gasps]

1055
01:38:20,250 --> 01:38:24,375
And that maybe those
"angels" are monuments

1056
01:38:24,458 --> 01:38:27,708
to every one of the people
who've heard His Voice

1057
01:38:27,791 --> 01:38:32,291
and sacrificed themselves
to do what was right.

